{"tid":2148030,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"泫雅完美駕馭騎呢時尚　　將泳衣穿在牛仔褲外面一樣性感度爆燈","createTime":"2020-08-09T15:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T06:08:05.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"45673758df1b75d51332501cf3dae89aab46ed62","tid":2148030,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T15:56:09.000Z","msg":"有「性感小野馬」之稱的韓國女歌手泫雅，過去推出的歌曲《Bubble Pop》、《Red》、《Lip &amp; Hip》及《Flower Shower》等等都起一股模仿熱潮，日前她在Instagram無預警下突然劇透，上載一段未公開的新歌MV片段，片段中的泫雅氣場十足展示出多個火辣舞蹈動作令粉絲興奮不已，不過最吸引眾人眼球的，就是她竟然將白色鏤空泳衣穿在長牛仔褲外面，極騎呢的造型都能被她完美駕馭。<br />\n<br />\n泫雅過往的回歸風格大多數都走性感路線，今次亦毫無懸念大跳惹火舞蹈動作，做出大膽摸胸和摸大髀的動作之餘亦大展S形身材，令人看到臉紅心跳。<br />\n<br />\n相比起火辣舞蹈動作，泫雅的造型亦成為焦點。她將鏤空泳衣穿在牛仔褲出面，看似騎呢仍完美營造出時尚感覺，這個獨特又新鮮的造型又會否帶來一股新潮流？"},{"pid":"d5e515bc15dfa2f487bcaee63953807c1db56812","tid":2148030,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T15:56:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200809/369186620240433152.jpeg/ud92c9_IRtU73JMpaDptG-vnCe5B2S2fDuD9nw7g_Z8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200809%2F369186620240433152.jpeg%2Fud92c9_IRtU73JMpaDptG-vnCe5B2S2fDuD9nw7g_Z8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=6c0dbb14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200809/369186617925177345.jpeg/b-1-L743NAOG0wnKU32ib4DAXJps3fvXN7dSije3Uoo?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200809%2F369186617925177345.jpeg%2Fb-1-L743NAOG0wnKU32ib4DAXJps3fvXN7dSije3Uoo%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=adb847af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bb12d53adbacf220158391061434b0cd96a9e82","tid":2148030,"uid":256952,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T15:58:58.000Z","msg":"收檔啦好心佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32834509553a2264f599074a61d2225420cb1db",